===================================================
EcBuild - ECMWF build system
===================================================

For detailed installation and usage instructions see the Manual.pdf document packaged with these sources.

An updated version of those instructions can also be found at 
http://software.ecmwf.int/wiki/display/SUPINF/ECMWF+Build+System

=============
QUICK INSTALL
=============

1. Extract the source files

 tar zxvf ecbuild-1.0.4-Source.tar.gz -C /path/to/install

2. Use cmake and point the module path to the installed source.

 cmake -DCMAKE_MODULE_PATH=/path/to/install [...]

